OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777381871
OL,3,CAsbestos experts called in after
OL,4,C'disgusting' pile of waste dumped on
OL,5,Cmajor road
OL,7,FA fly tip containing roofing
OL,8,Fmaterials, corrugated iron and
OL,9,Fasbestos has been dumped near Alton.
OL,11,FThe tip was reported earlier this
OL,12,Fmonth - just off the road next to the
OL,13,FA31 junction with Selbourne Road.
OL,15,FSpecialist asbestos experts have been
OL,16,Fcalled in to help clear the waste and
OL,17,Flook for evidence of where it came
OL,18,Ffrom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
