OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777381871
OL,3,CAsbestos experts called in after
OL,4,C'disgusting' pile of waste dumped on
OL,5,Cmajor road
OL,7,FEast Hampshire District Council says
OL,8,Fit's expected to cost thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds to clear.
OL,11,FCouncillor Tony Costigan, East
OL,12,FHampshire District Council portfolio
OL,13,Fholder for Neighbourhood Quality,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Everyone knows that asbestos is
OL,15,Fa particularly dangerous material
OL,16,Fwhich can cause serious lung
OL,17,Fconditions if inhaled and needs to be
OL,18,Fdisposed of safely.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777381871
OL,3,CAsbestos experts called in after
OL,4,C'disgusting' pile of waste dumped on
OL,5,Cmajor road
OL,7,F"Whoever has done this clearly doesn't
OL,8,Fcare about the danger it poses and has
OL,9,Fdumped this by the side of a road
OL,10,Frather than arranging proper disposal.
OL,12,F"They probably also charged their
OL,13,Fcustomer extra and just kept the money
OL,14,Fthey should have spent.
OL,16,F"It's disgusting.
OL,18,F"I encourage anyone who might have
OL,19,Fseen it being dumped or recognises the
OL,20,Fmaterials in the fly tip to get in
OL,21,Ftouch."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
