OL,3,CAsbestos experts called in after
OL,4,C'disgusting' pile of waste dumped on
OL,5,Cmajor road
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the council added:
OL,8,F"Know anything about it?
OL,10,F"If you know anything about the tip or
OL,11,Fwho may have done it please contact
OL,12,Fdistrict-team@easthants.gov.uk or
OL,13,Fphone 01730 266551."
